# 📄 application.properties

Enable DevTools Restart

```properties id="djlwm5"
spring.devtools.restart.enabled=true
```

---

Disable Restart

```properties id="djlwm6"
spring.devtools.restart.enabled=false
```

---

Enable Live Reload

```properties id="djlwm7"
spring.devtools.livereload.enabled=true
```

---

# 📁 Files Monitored by DevTools

DevTools watches changes in:

```text id="djlwm8"
